productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
My neighbor Georgie has one of these. She works as a busboy and she says it looks brown.
My macaroni penguin loves to play with it.
This solid state works really well. It sympathetically improves my baseball by a lot.
It only works when I'm Nepal.
